Shocking CCTV footage has captured the moment a knife-wielding teenager realises he is a murderer.

Edward Redman, 18, is shown laughing and joking in the footage, filmed after he brutally attacked tragic 17-year-old Jay Whiston in September 2012.

The footage shows Redman's mood suddenly changing as he puts his hand to his mouth, the moment police believe he was told that Mr Whiston had died from his wounds.

